claim.claim-text:
38. The system of claim 37 wherein said controller is adapted to be powered by a dc power system of the vehicle, said controller comprising a microprocessor-based controller operable to respond for system control to one or more of the following external inputs to said controller: 
1. Vehicle Ignition Status (On/Off); 
2. Pressure Sensor Inputs (Right/Left turn); 
3. Actuator Piston Position Encoder; 
4. Vehicle Speed Sensor; 
5. Steering column torque sensor; and 
6. Steering column position sensor.
